{
  "stem": "17720.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to give concerts in a number of cities inside with other not only instrumentalists, but also vocalists.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They came from the-- soloists from the opera.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And like that, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] organizing or arranging a number of multimedia concerts in different portion of Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, when came, however, after a certain period of time-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what happened-- happened something very strange.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Since I had some cousins that were living outside of the country-- I had one, my uncle, living in Paris.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was brother of my father, younger brother of my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "His name was Marcel [NON-ENGLISH] Polidi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When he understood that he have one very talented nephew, he organized one concert of mine in Paris in Salle Gaveau.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Even I received in my home copy of the arrangements, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they never allow me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The government, meaning concert direction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That one half of the concert direction was the police part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were under the control of the police, also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I already returned back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The second event that happened in that time was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in Bulgaria, when the time came one of the greatest conductors of our time, Herman Abendroth.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the conductor of the Berlin Radio, Radio Symphony Orchestra.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He heard me playing when he was visiting in Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I received invitation to become second concertmaster in his orchestra in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, by unknown reasons, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they sold this contract that he sended from there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything disappear.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was sended a number of letters there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all the time, the reply was that I was deadly sick, very badly sick.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
